  {
    "tag": "h3",
    "innerHtml": "Foreword"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "THIS little volume (the result of meditation and experience) is not\nintended as an exhaustive treatise on the much-written-upon subject\nof the power of thought. It is suggestive rather than explanatory,\nits object being to stimulate men and women to the discovery and\nperception of the truth that—"
  },
  {
